그들이 성공한 이유:

 - 쿠키 커터 개념이 없습니다.
 - 그들은 독특한 개성을 가지고 있습니다.
 - 멤버가 4명뿐이라 궁극의 편견이 있어도 다른 멤버들을 간과할 수 없다.
 - 말도 안되게 잘 훈련되고 무대 위에서 카리스마가 넘치며 각자의 강점을 보여줄 수 있습니다.
 - 그들은 매우 아름답습니다.
 - 그들은 당신이 그들의 여행의 일부가되고 싶게 만듭니다.
 - YG는 당신을 그리워하게 만들고 매번 컴백할 때마다 전달합니다.

author: @minihyunavillain2679
text: Jisoo es la más misteriosa entre los cuatro, por eso estoy tan interesado en ella. Sabemos que Jennie es una gran intérprete desde que era aprendiz, Lisa es una bailarina talentosa de Tailandia y Rose es una aspirante a cantante a la que le encanta tocar la guitarra. Por supuesto, hay más historias asombrosas sobre ellos, pero Jisoo, ella es tan difícil de descifrar. Realmente creo que hay más en ella de lo que parece y creo que Teddy dice que es una chica muy inteligente es realmente cierto. Siempre pienso que se adapta  como actriz y como ídolo y estoy muy contenta de que su actuaccion alla sido destaca y muy buena en el drama. Y creo que es una persona extremadamente talentosa: habla muy bien en público, sabe cómo llevar una conversación con extraños, es modelo, aspirante a escritora, como dijo en su documental, y ahora es cantante. Yo no tengo muchos talentos y me pone celoso de ella porque también tiene una cara muy hermosa. Espero que todos los seguidores y me incluyo que a Kim Jisoo la apoyen en todo. Es posible que no obtengamos una carrera en solitario de ella como miembro de Blankpink y eso está bien siempre que obtenga todo el crédito que se merece una vez que se convierta en una verdadera actriz y idols reconocida como se merece por que para mi es el ace escondido de blackpink ¡Estoy tan emocionada por ella!

author: @Anthony_Gx
text:
Im so happy with this entire CB. The video  the dancepractice/choreo! The record breaking :)))
The different vibe yet still BPsound! SOOO COOLL and lit!

Next single we gonna need more Rosé tho! honestly. This was more focused on the rap-line. Hip hop vibes. Bringing jennie back to remind everyone she is main rapper. Lisa + jennie side by side.... 
and i'm not gonna be ungrateful nor will i complain. Coz I love this. And I think it's everything Blinks needed and expected. 
But thankfully there's also a lead/main single. Title track for the album....Rosé can be sweet (coz that's her personality and she's genuinely a kind soul). But let's not forget she is lead dancer for a reason! ;-) She's FIERCE when she needs to be. And her voice is what gives BP that extra unique and recognizable sound! It can't be copied. Her voice is one of a kind. 
So I hope YG allows her to show off her strong side and her all-round talent in the next single. She can represent the PINK. But she has 0 problem representing the BLACK too!  I feel like in this video and choreo... Rosé was made to hold back a bit. And that's oke when it's a group and to allow others to shine. But I expect YG to come with something different next month, something where this time Rosé is able to show everyone her full potential! Just imagine BP (from debut till now) without Rosé for a second....and you'll instantly realize that would create an irreplacable gap that would take away an essential part of BP's uniqueness, sound and valued connection with (international -espescially western- ) fans/BLINKS!!! 
+ keep in mind that many BLINKS aren't K-pop fans/listeners at all, and only love BLACKPINK. That's coz the music and the 4 girls bringing it
BP is diffrent.Unique.Groundbreaking.Incomparable.OnceInALifetime.Worldwide.Special.Valuable.A class on it's own! Impossible to recreate. And they've established themselves as a solid, respected name throuhout the music industry (maybe internationally even more than just in the K-pop scene). Keep doing what BP has been doing so far, coz that's what we want! And PLEASEEEE give us some big, fat, excessive, obvious, thick, in-our-face,over the top CHAELISA in the next single :D:D <3 Doesn't get more real and genuine than that. But no matter what; more ROSÉ is what we all need for the 2nd single to make it complete! x (long story i know... thnx 4 reading all the way to here)
